    "An accuracy of NER depends on the quality of training data and the linguistic features used in it.",
    "Despite its evident importance, NER remains a challenging endeavor due to complexity and variability of language.",
    "Some common challenges include:(1) Ambiguity: Words can have multiple meanings or belong to different categories based on context [37].",
    "For example: भारत ने मै च जीता.",
    "दिल्ली भारत की राजधानी है | In first sentence, Bharat represents as an organization while in next sentence it represents a location."
